Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.30,0:00:03.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好 卡萊多之星要開始了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:03.30,0:00:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看卡萊多之星的時候要儘量使房間明亮
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:05.80,0:00:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要離電視太近哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:11.50,0:00:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:13.00,0:00:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是編織出幻想色彩的光與音樂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.90,0:00:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常不可思議的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.33,0:00:24.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的觀眾都為之興奮和感動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:24.40,0:00:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界第一的娛樂表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.30,0:00:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是憧憬於那樣的舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.20,0:00:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一位少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.20,0:00:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命 救命 救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.29,0:00:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊…救命啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry……
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:51.90,0:00:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我的名字是夫魯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.30,0:00:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有被選中的人才能看的到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.00,0:00:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞臺的精靈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.50,0:01:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:00.60,0:01:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們就來看看到現在為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.10,0:01:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在卡萊多劇團上發生的各種戲劇性的事情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.40,0:02:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憧憬於卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:39.80,0:02:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從日本到來的少女 苗木野空 16歲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:42.80,0:02:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(終於到啦)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.70,0:02:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的面試絕對要合格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也要成為卡萊多劇團的一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.70,0:02:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一員 一員 一員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.20,0:02:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待著滿懷期望的她是一連串意想不到的突發事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.90,0:03:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.30,0:03:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.60,0:03:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具有天生的毅力和超群的運動神經的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.00,0:03:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總算突破了這一關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.80,0:03:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:13.30,0:03:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於到達了夢想中的卡萊多劇團 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.70,0:03:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 嚴重遲到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.50,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這裏嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.50,0:03:24.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太好了 就是這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:24.10,0:03:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 你是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.40,0:03:29.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 我是苗木野空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.50,0:03:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我遲到了 萬分抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.20,0:03:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面試剛剛結束啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.20,0:03:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃 我從日本專程來面試的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.00,0:03:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好 你上舞臺來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.20,0:03:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太感謝了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.30,0:03:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.60,0:03:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.30,0:03:50.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面試已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:52.00,0:03:53.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉•哈姆雷特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.80,0:03:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她本人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我遲到是有原因的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.70,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管發生什麼 舞臺表演都會按時開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:02.00,0:04:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請回吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能就這樣回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.40,0:04:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了 我無論如何都想進卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.40,0:04:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.80,0:04:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我小時候就崇拜卡萊多劇團的演員
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.30,0:04:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢境中都會出現的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.80,0:04:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不能取得面試機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.80,0:04:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,登上舞臺的夢想破滅了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.30,0:04:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開演了 你要不要來看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.60,0:04:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.20,0:04:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能幫你這些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.00,0:04:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.90,0:04:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.20,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,於是空就這樣參觀了舞臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.10,0:04:52.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.90,0:04:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,手扭傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.80,0:05:05.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由於空的一場誤會 使得出演者受傷了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時出現了意外的人物(你…為什麼會在這裏)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:08.10,0:05:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.70,0:05:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老 老闆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:12.80,0:05:14.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.50,0:05:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突如其來初演的機會
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.80,0:05:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不安和期待交錯的她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.80,0:05:29.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.30,0:05:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 換動作了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.20,0:05:36.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.30,0:05:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.50,0:05:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就無法控制身體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.10,0:05:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(兔子姐姐加油啊)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.40,0:05:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.40,0:06:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:00.00,0:06:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在必須做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.40,0:06:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.40,0:06:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 兔子姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.50,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 看不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.70,0:06:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.50,0:06:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.10,0:06:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓開
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶…猶利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.10,0:06:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要謝幕了記得要保持笑容哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.20,0:06:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.00,0:06:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表演結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.40,0:06:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於夢想中舞臺的初次表演的她…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.30,0:06:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也清楚吧 自己演的有多不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.00,0:06:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這兒沒有你的容身之地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.80,0:07:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.10,0:07:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.10,0:07:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(由她去)\N從小以來一直憧憬的卡萊多劇團
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.40,0:07:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的夢想會在這裏結束嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.20,0:07:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.80,0:07:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被錄取了哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.50,0:07:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.30,0:07:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒看面試就錄取她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.20,0:07:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總有一天 觀眾們會專門為看她而到這裏來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被老闆看中其才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.10,0:07:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於能夠入團了的空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.70,0:07:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是殘酷試煉的開始
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.30,0:08:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然你那麼喜歡掃除 也替我們幹了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(那剩下的就拜託你了 心情真好)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.60,0:08:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特例入團的空 其他團員對她非常冷淡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.40,0:08:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 卡萊多劇團中的大明星蕾拉\N提出了非常苛刻的要求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.40,0:08:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.40,0:08:15.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:17.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的黃金不死鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.50,0:08:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金不死鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.00,0:08:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是只有蕾拉才能做到的大絕技
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.00,0:08:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先說在前面 我並不認為你有資格站在這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.50,0:08:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了 我做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.10,0:08:40.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做出黃金不死鳥給你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 真讓人期待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.79,0:08:51.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是做不出的話 就請離開這裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:51.00,0:08:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.20,0:08:56.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 空開始了拼死的特訓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:57.70,0:08:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要緊吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.70,0:09:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 沒事…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.50,0:09:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔下去的話一定要背向下 知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:10.20,0:09:11.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺動還不夠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.70,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再來一次
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.29,0:09:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是單純的擺動盪杆 卻這麼的困難
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:20.10,0:09:22.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我一定要做到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.70,0:09:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白天是舞臺的學習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.70,0:09:26.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上是拼命的訓練
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.70,0:09:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嚴酷的時間表
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.20,0:09:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,精神上 肉體上都快到達極限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.50,0:09:34.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣努力實在是太亂來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.29,0:09:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快下來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.00,0:09:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.79,0:09:47.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的拼命努力 與團內幾個團員結下了深厚的友情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.00,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點就成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這麼短的時間內能做到這種程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:49.79,0:09:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就只剩下一步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.50,0:09:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 現在的這些離完美的姿勢差得很遠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.70,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沒有抓住秋千之前 這根本就稱不上是黃金不死鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.00,0:10:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.10,0:10:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在明天之前 我絕對會完成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.79,0:10:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於命運的一天到來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.29,0:10:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很期待 她會讓我看到怎樣的黃金不死鳥呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.20,0:10:20.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能拼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相信自己
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.40,0:10:31.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於莽撞的空的挑戰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.29,0:10:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果失敗的話就立刻退團的壓力下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.60,0:10:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟能不能完成黃金不死鳥的大絕技呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.40,0:10:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的一生的大賭注開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.10,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的目標不是蕩杆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.60,0:11:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是重要的人-----羅米歐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:00.10,0:11:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.90,0:11:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要成為茱麗葉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.10,0:11:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金不死鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.80,0:11:08.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:16.70,0:11:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.70,0:11:25.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空…沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.60,0:11:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 謝謝你的關心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.00,0:11:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真讓我吃驚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.40,0:11:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然最後是失敗了…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.00,0:11:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但剛才的確實是黃金不死鳥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.80,0:11:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不認同也不行了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.20,0:11:41.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:41.50,0:11:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猶利 我們走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.80,0:11:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 你可以留在卡萊多劇團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.00,0:11:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 空真正成為了卡萊多劇團的一員了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.10,0:11:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之後 與好朋友安娜 米艾一起成功地完成了演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在自己的成長過程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.80,0:12:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶給了許多人們夢想和希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.40,0:12:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,法國的天才空竹少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.90,0:12:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 想不到天才的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.10,0:12:31.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼一會兒見
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:31.20,0:12:32.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期望你的優秀表現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.80,0:12:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特是很有自尊的天才少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.50,0:12:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在舞臺上表演出不愧為 空竹世界冠軍 的演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.80,0:12:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現了高級別的表演 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.50,0:12:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很厲害 但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.30,0:12:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像有種沒什麼意思的感覺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:58.10,0:13:02.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是緊密的空竹表演機器
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:02.10,0:13:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 好沒勁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.90,0:13:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的演出到今天為止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:10.40,0:13:13.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會遵守合同給你一星期的報酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:13.10,0:13:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你不必出場了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:17.30,0:13:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自尊受到傷害的羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.60,0:13:22.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想為她做點什麼的空…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.70,0:13:24.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有可能改變的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.10,0:13:28.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特也不是不能登臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.80,0:13:30.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.20,0:13:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也要一起登臺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:33.80,0:13:35.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.10,0:13:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我先走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.30,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好了 快點啊空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.50,0:13:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不會空竹啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.30,0:13:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡洛斯為什麼讓我和你一起練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.40,0:13:55.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完美的完成表演是當然的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.70,0:13:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失敗的話不如不做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.20,0:14:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.40,0:14:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對於羅傑特冷漠的言語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.50,0:14:04.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但空卻不放棄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.30,0:14:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,健 我要試試
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.00,0:14:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後野外舞臺…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,GO 約拿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.40,0:14:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.00,0:14:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 跳過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.40,0:14:24.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.80,0:14:31.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空好遜啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.30,0:14:33.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 加油啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.40,0:14:35.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.00,0:14:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議 對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.50,0:14:41.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看空的表演總要捏把汗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.00,0:14:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擔心她失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:43.70,0:14:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上她確實常常失敗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.60,0:14:48.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但有時卻有很精彩的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.80,0:14:52.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,象傻瓜般 卻又難以置信的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.40,0:14:57.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你該看看空的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.00,0:14:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空的…表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.50,0:15:05.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特第一次觀看了空的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.90,0:15:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發現了至今為止從來沒有看到過的觀眾的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.30,0:15:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我的表演完全不一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.60,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你來看我的演出嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.90,0:15:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我想和你一起演出空竹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.60,0:15:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.00,0:15:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就要開始空竹比賽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.90,0:15:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空竹世界冠軍羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.10,0:15:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家要看仔細哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.70,0:15:44.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Start
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.40,0:16:02.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 加油 空
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.60,0:16:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅傑特也不要輸啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.80,0:16:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,WINNER ---- 羅傑特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.30,0:16:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對觀眾的歡呼聲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.60,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“表演是為了讓觀眾高興而存在”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:29.60,0:16:33.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人深刻的銘記在心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.00,0:16:37.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多虧了空的魔法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:39.00,0:16:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.50,0:16:43.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空嚮往成為明星的路途又跨出了一大步
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.00,0:16:47.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在人魚公主的舞臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.50,0:16:51.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以自己天生的毅力和努力過關斬將
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.30,0:16:54.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為了嚮往已久的卡萊多劇團的主角
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.10,0:17:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太精彩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.40,0:17:02.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出色的完成了演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.80,0:17:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新的卡萊多之星啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:05.20,0:17:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看著她成長過來的蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.20,0:17:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於認同了空的實力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:12.00,0:17:13.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請多指教
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後終於…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:18.50,0:17:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與嚮往的蕾拉一起登臺演出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.30,0:17:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而 二人的實力差距太大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.00,0:17:26.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二人的呼吸怎麼也抓不准
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:25.20,0:17:27.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,(1 2 3   1 2 3)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.00,0:17:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:34.30,0:17:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而蕾拉卻採取了意外的行動…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.50,0:17:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.00,0:17:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.90,0:17:42.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐 那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.90,0:17:44.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走啦 蕾拉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.30,0:17:45.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:46.30,0:17:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.20,0:17:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從今天開始 我要住這裏一段時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.30,0:17:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.00,0:17:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.59,0:17:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來這裏是為了抓准你的呼吸和動作間隙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.06,0:18:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也請你的身體記住我的動作和呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.80,0:18:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐的動作和呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.90,0:18:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.00,0:18:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空 去食堂吃飯吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:09.90,0:18:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:11.50,0:18:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:13.09,0:18:16.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣突然開始了二人的共同生活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:16.90,0:18:21.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空一邊躊躇著 一方面又極力跟著蕾拉的步調
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:21.30,0:18:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.00,0:18:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離初演只剩一點點時間了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:29.20,0:18:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而離完成還有相當一段距離
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.40,0:18:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那時…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:35.00,0:18:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.30,0:18:37.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 太近了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.90,0:18:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.70,0:18:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得應該降低一下高潮部分的難度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.40,0:18:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是說簡單化高潮部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.20,0:18:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.00,0:18:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不同意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.20,0:18:50.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 但是蕾拉小姐…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.59,0:18:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決不允許簡單化高潮部分的表演
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.09,0:18:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我明天一天的時間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天要…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:05.00,0:19:06.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要開始特訓了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.50,0:19:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.50,0:19:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但一直像這樣重複練習
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.90,0:19:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,練出來的東西一定會變得非常無聊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.30,0:19:19.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾拉小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:19.80,0:19:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個可是我和你的真正決鬥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:23.00,0:19:26.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和蕾拉小姐真正的決鬥…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:26.00,0:19:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 接受嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:28.90,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.50,0:19:38.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣 賭上性命的真正決鬥開始了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:45.20,0:19:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好強的氣勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.60,0:19:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我覺得害怕的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的會被打落到海裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:50.50,0:19:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要是不小心 會變成鯊魚的美餐的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.40,0:20:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離初演開始還剩一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.10,0:20:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在狂風暴雨中蕾拉和空的決鬥更為激烈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.09,0:20:13.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好厲害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.10,0:20:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你快要支援不住了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.70,0:20:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
